data.description: This one-story home features an open living concept with 9 foot ceilings on the first floor. Gorgeous wood laminate flooring throughout the main living areas. Enjoy your open kitchen with granite, a large island with seating for four, tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. Come home and relax in your gorgeous master suite. You will never run out of space in the amazing master closet!! Enjoy your backyard your spacious covered porch! This home has all of the amenities you would expect in a BRAND NEW home!
